package.description:
A replacement for the default renderer of HTML_QuickForm that uses only XHTML and CSS but no table tags.

Usage: Just copy (and modify if you want) the stylesheet and do something like this:

require_once 'HTML/QuickForm.php';
require_once 'HTML/QuickForm/Renderer/Tableless.php';

$form =& new HTML_QuickForm();
$renderer =& new HTML_QuickForm_Renderer_Tableless();

// usual code, e.g. new form fields, rules, ...

$form->accept($renderer);
echo $renderer->toHtml();
